1. To retrieve the Ops Manager and Xenial Stemcell versions compatible with your <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %> version:

    ```
    curl -X GET https://support.broadcom.com/api/v2/products/pivotal-container-service/releases/RELEASE-ID/dependencies
    ```

    Where `RELEASE-ID` is the Broadcom Support ID for your <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %> version. 
